Looping Stement:
  For Loop
  While Loop
  
Looping Statement - It is used to perform same task for the required no.of.times and increase value for each tym of loop.

Range:
range(10) -> 0...9(Always starts from 0 and ends by n-1)
range(1,10) -> 1...9 (starts from 1 and ends by n-1))
range(1,10,2) -> 1,3,5,7,9 (starts from 1 and increment by 2 and ends by n-1))
